-----------------------------------------
What is Random Friend? 
-----------------------------------------
Random Friend is a Facebook Application *and* a Facebook Connect Web site.</b>
Displays the profile image of one of your Friends
Shows the Random Friend on your profile
Shows how to create an application with Java and JSP - including updating the profile.
Random Friend Site uses Facebook Connect to display the friend and publish a story to your profile

Random Friend Site
http://www.socialjava.com/random/connect.jsp 

Random Friend Application
http://apps.facebook.com/randomfriendapp  

-----------------------------------------
Random Friend Application 
-----------------------------------------
All files i same web directory:
http://www.socialjava.com/random/

-----------------------------------------
Facebook Application:
-----------------------------------------
index.jsp - callback URL in Facebook Application setup. Specified as http://www.socialjava.com/random/

-----------------------------------------
Facebook Connect Pages
-----------------------------------------
connect.jsp - for non-logged in users.  Shows FB Connect login button
showfriend.jsp - for connected and logged in users.  SHows Random Friend
xd_receiver.htm - required Facebook Connect file

-----------------------------------------
Web Site and include files for both apps:
-----------------------------------------
about.jsp - about page
header.html - include file header
intro.html - include file intro
footer.html - inlude file footer
randomfriendsmall.JPG - Logo

